  "_narrative": "**Where We Stand**\nWe're sitting at 0-0-0 with 0 points alongside everyone else in Pool C as the tournament begins. All four teams are starting fresh with everything to play for.\n\n**Our Next Game**\nWe face the Ennismore Eagles on Friday April 10th at 9:15 AM to kick off our tournament. Rankings suggest we match up well against the #25 Eagles, but they'll come out hungry and anything can happen in tournament hockey.\n\n**Around the Pool**\nAt the same 9:15 AM time slot, we'll want to keep an eye on Kincardine Kinucks (#3 seed) taking on Windsor Wildcats (#41 seed). Then at 3:45 PM, we play Windsor while Ennismore battles the top-seeded Kinucks. With our scenario analysis showing we win the pool in 156 out of 729 possible outcome combinations, there are plenty of paths forward if we take care of business.",
