    "talking_points": "**Mindset** \u2014 This is our first game at Provincials and we need to come out strong from the opening faceoff. Let's set the tone for our entire tournament with our energy, communication, and compete level right from the start.\n\n**Discipline** \u2014 We've got a clean slate heading into this tournament, so let's keep our penalties to a minimum and stay focused on playing our game. Smart, disciplined hockey will give us the best chance to control this game.\n\n**The Opponent** \u2014 Ennismore is here for a reason and they'll be looking to prove themselves against us. We need to respect their speed and work ethic while playing our structured system and supporting each other in all three zones.\n\n**What We Need** \u2014 Only the pool winner advances, so every point matters from game one. Let's focus on our forechecking pressure, moving the puck quickly, and being strong in front of our net to earn those crucial two points.",
